[bd8a216] by Abe Timmerman on Mon, 20 Apr 2015 12:08:15 +0200

     BUG FIX: strftime %F %T doesn't work everywhere :(

        At least Windows (and old HP-UX partially) do not undstand. Change
        to: %Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S


M	lib/Test/Smoke/LogMixin.pm
