[b082402] by abeltje on Sun, 8 Feb 2009 10:23:13 +0000

    
        * [FIX]
         * File::Spec->rel2abs() on windows strips relative elements (like
        ../) from the path, so as a trick we take the path relative to a
        peer directory. (Hysterical raisins)

